 Rhapsidion Snow for Patrons Cup 

 SRIMAX

 Bangalore: S. Padmanabhan-trained Rhapsidion Snow, who is in the pink of condition, may lift the Patrons Cup, the feature event at the races here on Thursday. Badge Of Gold is likely to go close to the four-year-old filly by Placerville out of Si Senorita.

